{"tid":2316871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳洲反滲透新法案通過 維多利亞州「一帶一路」面臨撤銷","createTime":"2020-12-08T07:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T09:18:09.000Z","uid":115608,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"849324d823929bb394ef78d0f06845a6e2b29297","tid":2316871,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"聯邦政府就遏制外國影響的提出的最新議案，已經在國會通過，維州與中國簽訂的「一帶一路」協議，可能遭到撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n新修訂的法案今日在參議院通過，容許聯邦政府審查並撤銷州、領地、市議會及公立大學與其他國家訂立的協議。外長可以評估政府或公立大學與外國政府之間的安排，檢查是否符合外交政策目標。<br />\n<br />\n財長費登堡（Josh Frydenberg）在回應記者的提問時表示，對於維州的有關協議，聯邦政府「最初不同意，現在仍然不同意，毫無疑問，我們將在適當時候做出決定」。<br />\n<br />\n法案關於權利與義務的主體法律在上星期通過，今日修訂議案在參議院通過。<br />\n<br />\n在最終表決前，獨立參議員帕特里克（Rex Patrick）未能獲得參議院足夠支持，無法將他提出使部長的決定受到司法審查的修訂，加入議案。<br />\n<br />\n中國方面曾經指這項法案，是損害中方與澳洲關係的14項爭端之一。外交部長派恩（Marise Payne）表示，該法例為各州和領地地政府，提供與聯邦就國際接觸進行磋商的機制。<br />\n<br />\n她說，這可能對澳洲的外交關係產生實質影響。<br />\n派恩表示：「參與度提高以及21世紀戰略複雜性增加，帶來了更大的風險，需要更多的磋商和努力，確保各州及領地與聯邦的外交政策保持一致。」<br />\n<br />\n聯邦政府將每年會就外長的決定向國會報告。<br />\n<br />\n外交及貿易部已經成立新的工作小組，以實施新法律。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/federal-government-s-bill-to-veto-deals-with-foreign-nations-passes-parliament?fbclid=IwAR3GdvDc421CLGhvhMcJuZY_2NIDOIZN73ev4wrhoo9O0V7TT7zrFYD-euQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Ffederal-government-s-bill-to-veto-deals-with-foreign-nations-passes-parliament%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3GdvDc421CLGhvhMcJuZY_2NIDOIZN73ev4wrhoo9O0V7TT7zrFYD-euQ&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=6d494ab6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/federal-government-s-bill-to-veto-deals-with-foreign-nations-passes-parliament?fbclid=IwAR3GdvDc421CLGhvhMcJuZY_2NIDOIZN73ev4wrhoo9O0V7TT7zrFYD-euQ</a>"},{"pid":"a56c30ffa37f5cf17d047373eb01510cd0ba068f","tid":2316871,"uid":173271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"索性沒收埋支酒商資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4933970dee64d926b0e9a3b9b8914dc136ec8c2f","tid":2316871,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503cac574d6af58a80e6304cae34809c5817b491","tid":2316871,"uid":11454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"入box hill 捉中共間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c056165e8d65180edbe386f86dde658969fd4a9","tid":2316871,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432a79d4704b66814f28f82a19e1cdb27ca7d5ef","tid":2316871,"uid":331590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"光復澳洲 成個島比支那買左仲唔做野就玩完嫁喇"},{"pid":"b5dad3639ff20da98999f74e14d129025b36e6e9","tid":2316871,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"503cac574d6af58a80e6304cae34809c5817b491","tid":2316871,"uid":11454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"入box hill 捉中共間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"ChinaDan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea8ae03394dee39e6ec1f9133f6cabed8dfe411","tid":2316871,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"Fuck dictator Dan"},{"pid":"b3384b476f6b4e37ff924d90f5f29cda5030ee8d","tid":2316871,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"回血"},{"pid":"5ac2eb911f6e6f8300788c66a2e685a492da320b","tid":2316871,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"